[src:text-summarization/natural-language-processing] Also, given that words in the same language are spoken by people with different accents, the speech recognition software must be able to recognize the wide variety of input as being identical to each other in terms of its textual equivalent.
[src:text-summarization/natural-language-processing] Given a sound clip of a person or people speaking, separate it into words.
[src:text-summarization/natural-language-processing] Given a text, transform those units and produce a spoken representation.
[src:text-summarization/natural-language-processing] Text-to-speech can be used to aid the visually impaired.
